  <title translate="true">CSUB Example: Solver Options</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">CSUB Example: Solver Options</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Next we will set the options for the MODFLOW 6 solver package. Select </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Model|MODFLOW Packages and Programs</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and go to the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Solvers</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> Pane. On the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Nonlinear</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab, override the value of </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Outer HClose</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and set its value to 10</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">-6</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. Also override the Outer maximum iterations and Under-relaxation scheme and set them to 100 and None respectively. On the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Linear</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab, override the values of Inner maximum iterations, Inner HClose, Inner RClose, Linear acceleration, and Relaxation factor. Set their values to 300, 10</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">-6</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">, 0.01, BICGSTAB, and 0.97 respectively. Click OK to close the dialog box when you are done. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleNonLinearOption.png" scale="60.00%" width="470" height="353" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">CSUB Example: Nonlinear solver options</title></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleLinearOptions.png" scale="60.00%" width="470" height="353" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">CSUB Example: Linear solver options</title></image></para>
  </body>
